{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-56","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-express-disagreement","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Asynchronous work</span> znači da zaposleni ne moraju da rade u isto vreme. Mogu završavati zadatke u različitim terminima prema svom rasporedu. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Asynchronous work allows remote teams to collaborate across different time zones.</span> – Timovi mogu da sarađuju u različitim vremenskim zonama bez potrebe da budu istovremeno na mreži.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Flexibility</span> znači da zaposleni imaju veću kontrolu nad radnim vremenom, što olakšava usklađivanje privatnih i profesionalnih obaveza. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Remote work offers flexibility in managing your schedule.</span> - Zaposleni mogu da izaberu vreme rada umesto da prate stroge kancelarijske sate.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-56"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja je prednost asinhronog rada prema Anni?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Zahteva da svi rade u isto vreme.</p>","feedback":"<p>Asinhroni rad omogućava zaposlenima da rade u različito vreme, a ne istovremeno.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Inatoa unyumbufu.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Inaondoa haja ya mawasiliano.</p>","feedback":"<p>Asinhroni rad i dalje uključuje komunikaciju, ali ne u realnom vremenu.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Čini raspored rada strožim.</p>","feedback":"<p>Asinhroni rad je suprotnost strogom rasporedu.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room3.png","characters":[{"character":"Anna","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"B1_11-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":9.34,"finishTimestamp":13.86},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Anna","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Anna","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":5.52,"dialogue":{"text":"I see where you're coming from, David. But we found that asynchronous remote work offers flexibility.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Anna","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":6.02,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 56","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-express-disagreement","dashedName":"task-56","certification":"b1-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-express-disagreement","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-57","prevChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-55","id":"67af5d21d2ffb218c43c89b3","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-56"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}